room_title: Escape room "Arizona Shootout" by Escapology St. Peters in St. Louis
room_address: 4105 N. Cloverleaf Dr. Suite B St. Peters, MO 63376
room_description:
Tombstone, Arizona, October 26, 1881.
You were just brainstorming with the group of local sheriffs to develop a new plan to round up the cowboy outlaw when you heard the screams. Quickly you pull out your gun and shoot one of the outlaws. The other two manage to vanish into thin air... Can you identify them in an hour, before they slip through your fingers?
